main event: Multiple sightings of unidentified flying objects occurred on May 30, 1966, with reports of bright lights traveling rapidly.
interesting points: The objects changed in luminosity from white to greyish,The second object was observed to be moving faster than a jet,The sighting lasted approximately 5 minutes and was made during daytime,Several witnesses reported additional observations,One witness described two objects, one appearing to chase the other.
sighted object: two or three bright flying objects
witness description: The witness reported observing bright lights with no sound, utilizing colors like red and white.
